                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.4215 Air Pollution/414: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Canada (<persName type="from">Boal</persName>)</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-04-19T17:00:00-05:00"
                            >April 19, 1933—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>15. Endeavor obtain from Canadian Government answer to inquiry stated in
                    Department’s telegram No. 9 of March 7, 6 p.m., 1933, Trail Smelter.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
